{
  "stem": "15694.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he was in the administration writing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we said, we came here actually as carpenters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We should have asked for something else, but soon we got a job as so-called carpenters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I was afraid what the Germans would think, because I never could hit a nail straight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But I was sort of like my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He was-- he knew everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He could do everything, being practical to excess almost.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And anyway, my job was nearby they had started a so-called cooling tower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Whatever the function of that is, I haven't learned, because I think it was bombed later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "With the only bomb that fell in Auschwitz, but I come to that later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was already about-- given work about six or eight meters high.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my father worked from the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But my work was to-- boards had been passed to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Though it was a-- a metal and steel skeleton of a tower we had surrounded with wooden planks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And my job was to get it from lower down and pass it to the person who nailed a screw in it to the next, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And so we had to work on, bit by bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Now, where I was working on, was about 5 centimeters, about two inches wide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Now, I could hold myself, because this tower was built that from one end to the other end, there were besides the level ones, there were on zig up, and zag going down, either girders.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the more I went to the middle, my hand was higher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I had to bend down at the same time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But the fellow next to me, he could at least hold himself on the previous board.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's-- then I remember the balancing act.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
